#Text=DS : That 's important for a lot of people - you see your audience .
#Text=You 're giving a lot of inspiration to a lot of people .
#Text=You do n't know who you might be inspiring to pursue music .
#Text=AN : [ Laughs ]
#Text=Oh , kids , do n't be like me ! I would definitely go with nature over man made .
#Text=DS : What 's your favorite curse word ?
#Text=AN : Fuck .
#Text=DS : What 's your favorite euphemism for breasts ?
#Text=AN : Big guns .
#Text=DS : Have you used that recently ?
#Text=AN : Actually , I think I did use that in the last week , and no comment .
#Text=DS : I read that you named the band after fast women and fast cars .
#Text=AN : [ Laughs ]
#Text=Who told you that ?
#Text=No , Bang Camaro were two words out of the English language that were the two sexiest words we could think of .
#Text=We put them together and they roll off the tongue .
#Text=Bang Camaro .
#Text=It says a lot more than it means .
#Text=DS : What sort of qualities do you look for in a woman ?
#Text=AN : I need a girl who is going to make me laugh .
#Text=I need a woman who is smarter than I am .
#Text=A woman who will always keep me guessing .
#Text=Absolutely .
#Text=Calling me out for my own jerky bullshit .
#Text=I like a girl who is fiercely independent , knows what she wants , and does n't need me .
#Text=DS : Hillary Clinton or Barack Obama ?
#Text=AN : Oh , man , I 'm going to get in a lot of trouble for saying Obama .
#Text=I would probably go with Obama .
#Text=There 's just something in his rhetoric and his oratory that is a lot more inspiring than Hillary .
#Text=Hillary , to me , represents not much of a changing of the guard .
#Text=DS : What would be the greatest of misfortunes to befall you ?
#Text=AN : [ Chuckles ]
#Text=Oh , if I were to die alone .
#Text=No , probably one of my greatest fears is injuring or maiming any of my appendages , to be honest .
#Text=DS : Do you have any special things you do to make sure you do n't injure or lose an appendage ?
#Text=AN : [ Chuckles ]
#Text=I do n't keep my hands in my pockets when I am running down stairs .
#Text=DS : That 's a conscious choice ?
#Text=AN : Yes , that 's a conscious choice .
#Text=DS : What if you are just walking down stairs ?
#Text=AN : [ Chuckles ]
#Text=You ca n't realign the stars , man .
#Text=Shit will happen , shit will happen .
#Text=DS : What possession do you treasure most ?
#Text=AN : That 's a good question .
#Text=Probably my cat .
#Text=I love my cat more than anything .
#Text=DS : What 's your cat 's name ?
#Text=AN : Sadie .
#Text=DS : Like Sexy Sadie ?
#Text=AN : Yeah , like Sexy Sadie .
#Text=That 's exactly what I named her after .
#Text=Big John Lennon fan , so I could n't resist .
